"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-simone-biles-responds-olympic-gesture-branded-disgusting-21372030\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles has defended her decision to bow forOlympicchampion Rebeca Andrade during a medal ceremony after oneNFLstar branded the act of sportsmanship 'disgusting'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles and fellow American gymnast Jordan Chiles bowed down to Olympic gold medallist Andrade after the Brazilian won the floor final inParis.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 186, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995789875371414, \"rank\": 0.0002622671539796268, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 254, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After claiming gold in three events in the French capital, Biles was going for a fourth victory buthad to settle for silver after making a couple of uncharacteristic mistakes during her routine.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 355, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.935824184194144, \"rank\": 0.06530817466672474, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was initially disappointed by the outcome but soon celebrated team-mate Chiles' bronze and paid tribute to Brazilian gymnast Andrade, producing one of the most iconic images of the Games.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast majority of fans praised Biles and Chiles for their sportsmanship but Baltimore Ravens cornerback Marlon Humphrey bizarrely called it 'disgusting'.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\", \"score\": 0.999999932772655, \"rank\": 4.286343703643624e-08, \"text\": \"Baltimore Ravens\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marlon Humphrey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is literally disgusting,' the 28-year-old posted on X, before adding: 'I am lowkey getting cooked right now.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am getting cussed out in Brazilian on Instagram lol.'\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0053196715794678e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking onNBC's TODAYshow, Biles defended the gesture and said it was important for the Americans to give Andrade her 'flowers'.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is everything.pic.twitter.com/FrXz7wWtQg  'I think it's all about sportsmanship, and we do not care whether we win or lose,' the 11-time Olympic medal winner said.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are always going to keep a good face and support our competitors because they have worked just as hard as we have for that moment.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So you have to give them their flowers.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's exactly what me and Jordan were doing, and we were so happy for her.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.8562038914213778, \"rank\": 0.09755623034182796, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She deserved it.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had the best floor routine of the day and in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's like, yeah, she deserved it.'\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a separate interview, Biles described Andrade as a 'queen' and said it was 'super-exciting' to be a part of the first all-black podium in men or women's gymnastics at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Rebeca's so amazing, she's a queen,' said Biles.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'She's such an excitement to watch and then all the fans in the crowd were always cheering for her, so it was just the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was an all-black podium so that was super-exciting for us, but then Jordan was like \\\"should we bow to her?\\\"\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.8562038914213778, \"rank\": 0.09755623034182796, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and I was like \\\"absolutely\\\".'\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade, meanwhile, appreciated the gesture from the American duo, saying: 'It was very cute of them.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9995789875371414, \"rank\": 0.0002622671539796268, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'They are the world's best athletes and what they did means a lot to me.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are always rooting for each other, the final is very difficult for everyone.'\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 is expected to be Biles' final Olympic Games but she has not ruled out competing in 2028 when the show heads to Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2630, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2495, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.500787515338239e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999710594243, \"rank\": 2.8846641589920432e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You know, you never say never,' she said.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The next Olympics is on home turf, so you just never know.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just gonna relax and see where life takes me.'\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics fans have another sign snatched during Taiwan and China medal ceremony  ArrowMORE:Olympian wins lifetime supply of ramen and macaroni cheese after winning gold in Paris  ArrowMORE:'It's a scandal!'\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9998618835194946, \"rank\": 0.0001302500120627359, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 2979, \"end\": 2990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Medal_(German_Empire)\", \"score\": 0.9998651067761388, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China medal\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Medal_(German_Empire)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Medal_(German_Empire)\"}, {\"begin\": 3092, \"end\": 3097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999138254, \"rank\": 8.615509925588257e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q4